## Option 2 — Use from the Terminal (no Python needed)

```bash
# Basic usage
python3 -m medextract.cli /path/to/photos

# With options
python3 -m medextract.cli /path/to/photos \
    --output my_readings.csv \
    --workers 4 \
    --image-size 768

# See all available options
python3 -m medextract.cli --help
```

